      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DIVA'S DELIGHT (7) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (23.84) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form here sound including eight wins. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Can make amends. YOUNG ENERGY (6) found trouble in the run at this course and distance last time and fell. May be worth another try. IMPATIENT ROSE (1) was among the minors three back at this track then missed the frame the last two, but drawn box 1 this time where she has won before. Safe beginner and drawn well on the inside. Has the ability and expected to do much better. FIREBALL ZED (4) continues to race well and is sure to be competitive again.",
